title: $:/plugins/rimir/cascade-palette/lens/caption-then-title
tags: $:/tags/rimir/cascade-palette/lens
ca-lens-name: Caption → Title
ca-lens-chip: 💬 Caption → Title
ca-lens-hint: Prefer caption; fall back to title when the row has no caption.
ca-lens-help: Projects the NAME slot — replaces each data row's display name with the row tiddler's ''`caption`'' when present, otherwise the bare title. Shipped as the default name lens so kind / data tiddlers read naturally in every menu and view without the asymmetry between caption-aware drills (e.g. ''Find entity'') and raw-title views (e.g. ''All tiddlers'').
ca-lens-name-filter: [<currentTiddler>get[caption]else<currentTiddler>]
ca-lens-default: name
ca-order: 50
